,"tid":14220,"uid":8329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前高登話北上食貓肉食狗肉，幾百個正評<br />\n唔知有無食佢呢啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係邊都未搞清就想抽水<br />\n正傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4900faf0d65c320356ee3fb01bcc6b9335df93c","tid":14220,"uid":45071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"冚家剷對呢啲人黎講只係輕罰<br />\n屌你老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}